channel.title: Can't get on my own server?!
channel.description:
Ok, recently, our hoster's internet shut off and he almost lost his house but I put the server back up 5 minutes ago but theres one issue.
I can't get on?!?
[img]http://i575.photobucket.com/albums/ss195/Mariokillu/Screenshot2.jpg[/img]
As you can see, the server is up and running but
[img]http://i575.photobucket.com/albums/ss195/Mariokillu/Screenshot3-1.jpg[/img]
I can't get on.
I checked everything. The ban list, ip ban list, the ip set for the client and reset my computer but still no luck.
Any suggestions?
